**Unibios Information:**
- Open neogeo.zip then copy the files to your rom .zip (this step is not needed if the BIOS files are already included in your rom).
- Download Unibios 3.2: http://unibios.free.fr/download.html
- Extract uni-bios.rom and rename it to sp-s2.sp1.
- Open your rom .zip and replace sp-s2.sp1 with the one from previous step.
- Add your game in hakchi2 and sync.
